channel.title: Freezer doors in Office Complex not working
channel.description:
Map: bm_c1a2c Position: -1408.257568 266.448151 216.131256;setang 15.455296 -85.5516
None of the doors in the freezer inside Office Complex will open or close apart from the one used to enter the freezer, though I can hear the sound effect.
